comment._content: Official List of Commissioned and Other Officers of the Public Health Service, 1916 books.google.com/books?id=_VfOAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA34 has Surg. R.L. Wilson in charge, and Assistant Surgeon A. R. Sweeney as officers at the Galveston (Texas) Quarantine Station.
